## `📝` Changelog - v0.1.2
*Updated on 2025/05/01*

### `🚀` New Features
- Added **1,540 new cards** featuring new characters.
  View the full list [here](https://anicatch.com/list.txt).

### `🛠️` Changes
- Rewritten parts of the UI to support the latest Discord component standards.
- The `/catch` command now uses the new Discord components.
- The `/animon` command now uses the new Discord components.
- The `/battle` command now uses the new Discord components.
- The `/collection` command now uses the new Discord components.
